<h1>Welcome to Nerdy.lol!</h1>
<h2>View a discussion on your favorite nerdy topic and add a post, or start a discussion of your own!</h2>

<% if @discussions.any? %>
<% @discussions.each do |discussion|%>
<li><%= link_to discussion.topic, discussion_path(discussion) %></li>
<% end %>
<% else %>
<p> No one has made a discussion yet. </p>
<% end %>

<p><%= link_to "Add new discussion", new_discussion_path %></p>